                    <p class="text-sm text-[#445E4F] mt-2">
                        Lorem ipsum is a dummy or placeholder text commonly used in graphic design.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex mt-4 space-x-4">
                        <a href="#" class="text-[#445E4F]">
